=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains the configuration information to customize the logo, font, and
color of an Amazon Q Business web experience with individual files for
each property or a CSS file for them all.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 CustomCSSUrl => Str

Provides the URL where the custom CSS file is hosted for an Amazon Q
web experience.


